  "instructions": [
    "Prepare the brine by mixing 1 cup of water, 1 tsp of salt, 1 tsp of brown sugar, and 1 tsp of black pepper in a bowl until the sugar and salt dissolve.",
    "Add the sea bass fillets to the brine and refrigerate for at least 2 hours or overnight.",
    "Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Gently remove the sea bass fillets from the brine and pat them dry with paper towels.",
    "Cut the sourdough bread into 1-inch cubes and toast until crispy.",
    "Cut the sea bass fillets into 1-inch pieces and sprinkle with lemon zest and sea salt.",
    "Assemble the finger sandwiches by spreading a layer of vegan butter on each toasted bread cube, then topping with a piece of sea bass, a sprinkle of chopped fresh dill and chives, and finally another bread cube.",
    "Garnish with a sprinkle of sea salt and a slice of lemon on top of each sandwich.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
  ],
